Doc: A type defining the characteristics of the gas being traded in a physically settled gas transaction.

Source.Contents:
/#
   A type defining the characteristics of the gas being traded in a physically settled gas transaction.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.GasProduct {
  # The type of gas to be delivered.
  type : string

  # The calorific value of the gas to be delivered, specified in megajoules per cubic meter (MJ/m3).
  calorificValue : decimal

  # The quality of the gas to be delivered.
  quality : string

}

type.Doc: The type of gas to be delivered.
type.Name: type

calorificValue.Doc: The calorific value of the gas to be delivered, specified in megajoules per cubic meter (MJ/m3).
calorificValue.Name: calorificValue

quality.Doc: The quality of the gas to be delivered.
quality.Name: quality
